{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji28.pdf"],"article":{"title":"关于章士钊荐用李的批语","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于章士钊荐用李?的批语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年5月24日）请周酌办。章士钊只荐此一人，似宜用之。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月二十四日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李自谓已六十六岁，有妻室之累，无儿可依，觉悟前非，力图晚盖，精力尚能做事，希望给予一工作。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]章士钊，当时任政协第一届全国委员会委员。[2]李悦，曾任国民党政府财政部次长。[3]周，指周恩来。[4]这段批语写在李党自传第一页上。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":5,"day":24}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":426,"page_end":426},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"批示"}]}]}